---
// Hero section — headline, subtext, CTA buttons, and image placeholder
---

<section class="bg-brand-cream">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Text Content -->
      <div class="reveal space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold leading-tight text-brand-brown">
          <span data-i18n="hero.headline1">Viste Tu Amor,</span><br />
          <span class="text-brand-orange" data-i18n="hero.headline2">Pinta Tu Vínculo</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-brown/80 max-w-md" data-i18n="hero.subtext">
          Sudaderas personalizadas con tu mascota y kits de pintura por números para celebrar el vínculo entre tú y tu mejor amigo peludo.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="#categories"
            class="bg-brand-brown text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-brand-orange transition-colors"
            data-i18n="hero.shopNow"
          >
            Comprar Ahora
          </a>
          <a
            href="#how-it-works"
            class="border-2 border-brand-brown text-brand-brown px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-brand-brown hover:text-white transition-colors"
            data-i18n="hero.howItWorks"
          >
            Cómo Funciona
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Hero Image -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-orange/20 rounded-3xl rotate-3"></div>
          <img
            src="/hero-green.png"
            alt="Person with dog"
            class="relative w-full rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
